Subject: Jobs in Use
Description:
Need help with getting the following:

- Day/Time and frequency of collection tasks run by Stealthbits
- What the collection is intended to address and purpose of the system being monitored
- Of the collected reports, which are we reviewing and acting on verses those where we are collecting but not actively using.
Solution_Comment__c: Customer created a spreadsheet and manually populated it with all their running jobs, when they run, what they do, and who receives them.
